1. User is watching normal Youtube video. 
2. User get notification of Youtube shorts video. 
3. On normal video mode user click on gear icon(settings) & it opens dialog with options to change video speed, audio track etc. 
4. Without dismissing the dialog, User click the YT short video notification.
5. It starts to play YT shorts video with settings dialog still on front. 

Actual - 
Settings dialog stays as is. 

Expected - 
Dialog should get dismiss automatically. 

Note - I am on latest version on android app at the time of reporting. 
Android 11 from Google. 
